title: Crazy Monday: Kalonzo Musyoka rides on cleric's blessings
text:
Your are here » Home » Kenya Kalonzo Musyoka rides on cleric's blessings By Gideon Maundu | Updated Mon, February 13th 2017 at 12:58 GMT +3 SHARE THIS ARTICLE Share on Twitter 
Bishop Daniel Indatula of the Jesus Winning Soul Ministry church in Migadini, Changamwe, attempts to carry Wiper leader Kalonzo Musyoka during a Sunday service in Mombasa County. 
The man of cloth blessed the Wiper leader and the significance of the demonstration was to show the former Vice President had been uplifted ahead of the August General Election. 
Wiper leader Kalonzo Musyoka and Bishop Daniel Indatula of the Jesus Winning Soul Ministry church.
